<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pterachaenia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pterachaenia" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Pterachaenia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. His statement &quot;I think this section will also turn out to be a separate genus (gen. proprium 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pterachaenia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pterachaenia" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Pterachaenia</taxonomicName>
)&quot; [translated from Russian] qualifies it, however, as a provisional genus name not formally accepted by its author.
</paragraph>
